ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Man City l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPep chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">100 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Man xanh \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, khi h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9. V\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u00ec sao m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0103n may g\u1eb7p th\u1eddi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng. N\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n, v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ec3 thua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 HLV n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh xa c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-chia-se-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed9i l\u1ed7i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Pep ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Community Shield, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. Champions League, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1. M\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Champions League l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Premier League&rdquo; &ndash; Pep chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8): Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai</span><br>\r\nChia tay Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tho\u00e1t d\u1edbp Juventus \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u00dd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u ngay...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\">3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi d\u00e0nh cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Blues d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ng\u1ed5n ngang nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2005","checkdouble":"193751"}]}